# Quickdraw Duel Demo (~20 seconds)
# Demonstrates: Two players face off in a quickdraw duel

# Wait for devices to initialize (device 0=Hunter, device 1=Bounty)
wait 2

# Trigger duel: send DUEL_REQUEST packet from device 0 to device 1
# Packet type 1 = DUEL_REQUEST
peer 0 1 1
wait 2

# Both players accept duel by pressing button
b 0
b 1
wait 2

# Wait for countdown (3 seconds)
wait 4

# Device 0 draws first and wins
b 0
wait 3

# Show final states
state
